00:41:44,302 --> 00:41:45,835
Snart!

710
00:41:45,837 --> 00:41:47,837
Bình tĩnh, Mick.

711
00:41:47,839 --> 00:41:51,074
Chuyện gì đang xảy ra vậy?

712
00:41:51,076 --> 00:41:52,442
Kế hoạch đó.

713
00:41:56,681 --> 00:41:59,015
Chào em gái.

714
00:42:00,784 --> 00:42:02,352
Ngon.

